---

<section class="lk-section lk-manifest" id="manifest" aria-labelledby="manifest-title">
  <div class="lk-container lk-manifest-inner">
    <p class="lk-eyebrow" data-reveal>Manifest</p>
    <h2 id="manifest-title" class="lk-h1 lk-manifest-text" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 160ms;">
      Wir entwickeln Lichtkonzepte für Räume,
      <span class="lk-display-italic" style="color: var(--color-lk-accent);">die Atmosphäre verlangen.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="lk-body lk-manifest-body" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 320ms;">
      Fitnessstudios. Showrooms. Praxen. Premium-Wohnräume. Wir verstehen, wann Licht
      Funktion sein muss, wann es Atmosphäre wird und wann es selbst zur Skulptur werden darf.
      Aus eigener Kollektion. Gemeinsam mit Studio Konzept und Boden Konzept.
    </p>

    <div class="lk-manifest-stats" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 480ms;">
      <div class="lk-stat">
        <span class="lk-stat-num">9</span>
        <span class="lk-label">Eigene Lichtsysteme</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lk-stat">
        <span class="lk-stat-num">Studio &nbsp;+ <br>Gewerbe</span>
        <span class="lk-label">Spezialisierung</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lk-stat">
        <span class="lk-stat-num">Made in <span class="lk-display-italic">Germany</span></span>
        <span class="lk-label">Bundesweit aktiv</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .lk-manifest {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lk-manifest-inner {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .lk-manifest-text {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lk-manifest-body {
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lk-manifest-stats {
    margin-top: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-lk-line);
    padding-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  .lk-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lk-stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-lk-fg);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .lk-manifest-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
